               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. CLERK</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18530404-name-538" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-538" type="surname" value="EDWARDS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-538" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD EDWARDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am waiter at the Duke's Head, at Putney. On 7th March the prisoner came, about half-past 2 o'clock in the afternoon—</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185304040147"></xptr>
               <p>he called for half a pint of porter, and gave in payment a shilling—I told him it was a bad one—my mistress came to the bar, and told me to fetch a policeman—I went, but could not find one—the prisoner was just going out when I came back—my mistress said she had forgiven him, as he spoke so innocently—I kept the shilling, and afterwards gave it to the policeman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18530404-name-539" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-539" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-539" type="surname" value="WEEDON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-539" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEEDON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, V</hi> 337). I produce the shilling I received from the last witness.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18530404-name-540" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-540" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-540" type="surname" value="NEWINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-540" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT NEWINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a baker, at Richmond. On 17th March the prisoner came to my shop, about a quarter past 4 o'clock, for a 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., biscuit—I gave it him; he gave me a bad shilling; I gave him the change, but I took it back, and told him it was bad—I asked him if he had got any more; he said, "No"—I took back the change and the biscuit, and sent for a constable—I gave him the shilling, and gave the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18530404-name-541" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-541" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
