                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-541" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY HERNON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, V</hi> 297). I was called to Mr. Newin's shop on 17th March, in the afternoon, and took the prisoner—I found nothing on him—I received the shilling from Mr. Newins</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18530404-name-542" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-542" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
