                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-542" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint. These are both counterfeit shillings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I had the shillings in my possession, but was not aware that they were bad.</p>
